		"description": "<p>Also at 3rd level, unlike other scholars, you interweave a study of the arcane directly into your greater search for knowledge. You have the ability to cast spells, following the normal rules for spellcasting.</p>\n<h2>Cantrips</h2>\n<p>At 3rd level, you know two cantrips of your choice from the wizard spell list. These spells count as scholar spells for you. You learn an additional cantrip at 10th level.</p>\n<h2>Spell Slots</h2>\n<p>The Hedge Mage Spellcasting table shows how many spell slots you have to cast your spells of 1st-level and higher. To cast one of these spells, you must expend a slot of the spell&rsquo;s level or higher. You regain all expended spell slots when you finish a long rest.</p>\n<p><strong>Table: Hedge Mage Spells</strong></p>\n<table style=\"width: 100%; height: 350px;\" border=\"1\"><colgroup><col style=\"width: 21.5953%;\"><col style=\"width: 30.1556%;\"><col style=\"width: 10.7004%;\"><col style=\"width: 13.8132%;\"><col style=\"width: 12.0623%;\"><col style=\"width: 11.6732%;\"></colgroup>\n<thead>\n<tr style=\"text-align: center; height: 47.6px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 47.6px;\">Level</td>\n<td style=\"height: 47.6px;\">\n<p>Cantrips</p>\n<p>Known</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"height: 47.6px;\">1st</td>\n<td style=\"height: 47.6px;\">2nd</td>\n<td style=\"height: 47.6px;\">3rd</td>\n<td style=\"height: 47.6px;\">4th</td>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr style=\"height: 16.8px; text-align: center;\">\n<td style=\"height: 16.8px;\">3rd</td>\n<td style=\"height: 16.8px;\">2</td>\n<td style=\"height: 16.8px;\">2</td>\n<td style=\"height: 16.8px;\">-</td>\n<td style=\"height: 16.8px;\">-</td>\n<td style=\"height: 16.8px;\">-</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 16.8px; text-align: center;\">\n<td style=\"height: 16.8px;\">4th</td>\n<td style=\"height: 16.8px;\">2</td>\n<td style=\"height: 16.8px;\">3</td>\n<td style=\"height: 16.8px;\">-</td>\n<td style=\"height: 16.8px;\">-</td>\n<td style=\"height: 16.8px;\">-</td>\n</tr>\n<tr s